  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world overrun by the undead, the Hollow Monks have emerged—ethereal warriors with only robes and a singular purpose: to eradicate the <strong>Nasty Zombies</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight solo or with up to 4 players, uncover hidden secrets, and unlock over 100 achievements. Master intuitive melee combat and a diverse arsenal of firearms, and enhance your abilities by unlocking <strong>Blessings</strong> and <strong>Miracles</strong> between runs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After unlocking everything, <strong>Prestige </strong>to prove your mastery—each <strong>Prestige</strong> level increases the number of <strong>Blessings</strong> you can equip at once, letting you build even deadlier loadouts. Climb the <strong>Leaderboards</strong>, competing for <strong>Highest Wave, Fastest Speedruns, and Top Prestige ranks</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/45e037a70692ed4b9c8c8a22e072469c.avif?t=1773522283\" width=616 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/0792342628bdae63af120c3238609315.poster.avif?t=1773522283\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/0792342628bdae63af120c3238609315.webm?t=1773522283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/0792342628bdae63af120c3238609315.mp4?t=1773522283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The classic wave-based zombie survival formula you know and love—amped up with high-speed movement and a retro twist.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/69f12c65bc42e7e29d3b0defcc7f8d29.avif?t=1773522283\" width=616 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/5c298ff013bb2d955a3359212bdfe290.poster.avif?t=1773522283\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/5c298ff013bb2d955a3359212bdfe290.webm?t=1773522283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/5c298ff013bb2d955a3359212bdfe290.mp4?t=1773522283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Master a fast-paced movement system where agility is your greatest weapon! Harness the Kinetic Energy system, gaining increased firepower and melee speed as you stay on the move. Leap over obstacles, slide under walls, and air dash to outmaneuver the undead!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/8370b5d4fe871cccb0ba57e8ba8574c5.avif?t=1773522283\" width=616 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/005f7b7e49b8b86d2787cfeaa2b08289.poster.avif?t=1773522283\" width=616 height=293 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/005f7b7e49b8b86d2787cfeaa2b08289.webm?t=1773522283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Experience <strong>endless replayability</strong> with dynamically generated map layouts that change every match. No two runs are ever the same—adapt to shifting environments, discover new pathways, and strategise on the fly as you fight to survive the undead horde.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/b29c8d352eaec70b439b96c902eb2373.avif?t=1773522283\" width=616 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/34a4ff6a2877c63b86e5d29d23e2d8f4.poster.avif?t=1773522283\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/34a4ff6a2877c63b86e5d29d23e2d8f4.webm?t=1773522283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/34a4ff6a2877c63b86e5d29d23e2d8f4.mp4?t=1773522283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Earn money by killing zombies, then spend it on <strong>Blessings</strong> and <strong>Miracles</strong>.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are <strong>13 Blessings</strong> and <strong>9 Miracles</strong> to choose from.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Blessings</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bandolier:</strong> Increased Ammo Storage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Carpenter:</strong> Repair Barricades Faster & More Securely</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gunslinger:</strong> Weapons Have Reduced Recoil, Switch Faster & Reload Whilst Holstered</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hardened Flesh:</strong> Increased Health</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kinetic Recovery:</strong> Kinetic Energy Reduces Health Regeneration Delay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Miracull:</strong> Miracles Are Twice as Frequent, but Their Duration Is Reduced</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Monotome: </strong>Increase Firearm Damage and Penetration Instead of Equipping Two Firearms</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rapid Reload:</strong> Reload Faster</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retribution:</strong> Explosive Second Chance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ruction:</strong> Starter Weapons are Stronger</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scavenger:</strong> Scavenge Ammo from Dead Zombies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vengeance:</strong> Explode Attacking Zombie's Head</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Z-Ray Vision:</strong> See Zombies, Miracles & Scavenger Packs Through Walls</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Miracles</strong></u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nuke:</strong> Kill All Zombies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Max Ammo:</strong> Refill All Ammo & Kinetic Energy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Insta-Kill:</strong> Zombies Die in One Hit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bottomless Clip:</strong> Unlimited Ammo & Kinetic Energy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Necrovore:</strong> Inflicted Damage Heals You</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zillionaire:</strong> Receive a Burst of Money & Double Money</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vitality Surge:</strong> Boost Your Health & Speed Above Max & Continuously Regenerate Health</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fortify:</strong> Repairs & Electrifies All Barricades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chronopulse:</strong> Time Slows in Proximity to Zombies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/105346f53aa1b2b79cb377e74ad06650.avif?t=1773522283\" width=616 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/3a963ac5ef24f826c460b8600d1d7063.poster.avif?t=1773522283\" width=633 height=460 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851700/extras/3a963ac5ef24f826c460b8600d1d7063.webm?t=1773522283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Track your stats and compete for your place on the global leaderboards.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Leaderboards:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prestige Leaderboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Highest Wave Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speedrun Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Map & Game Mode Specific Leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
